s Character Pack |date=October 23, 2018|accessdate=October 16, 2019|author= Gerardo Gutierrez|website=Bricks to Life}}</ref>\n\n== Notes ==\n{{Notelist|refs=\n\n<!-- Infobox -->\n\n{{efn|name=alias|A previous alias.}}\n\n{{efn|name=affiliation|A previous affiliation.}}\n\n}}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist|refs=\n\n<!-- Storyline -->\n\n<ref name=\"Pilot ep\">{{Cite episode |title=Pilot |episode-link=Pilot (Arrow) |series=Arrow |series-link=Arrow (TV series) |network=[[The CW]] |season=1 |number=1 |airdate=October 10, 2012}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Lone Gunmen ep\">{{Cite episode |title=Lone Gunmen |episode-link=Lone Gunmen (Arrow) |series=Arrow |series-link=Arrow (TV series) |network=[[The CW]] |season=1 |number=3 |airdate=October 24, 2012}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"The Odyssey ep\">{{Cite episode |title=The Odyssey |episode-link=The Odyssey (Arrow) |series=Arrow |series-link=Arrow (TV series) |network=[[The CW]] |season=1 |number=14 |airdate=February 13, 2013}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"The Undertaking ep\">{{Cite episode |title=The Undertaking |episode-link=The Undertaking |series=Arrow |series-link=Arrow (TV series) |network=[[The CW]] |season=1 |number=21 |airdate=May 1, 2013}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"IGN Amell interview\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/05/30/arrow-star-stephen-amell-talks-about-playing-tvs-new-oliver-queen |title=Arrow Star Stephen Amell Talks About Playing TV's New Oliver Queen |last=Goldman |first=Eric |date=May 30, 2012 |publisher=IGN |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222061455/http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/05/30/arrow-star-stephen-amell-talks-about-playing-tvs-new-oliver-queen |archive-date=February 22, 2014 |access-date=November 13, 2013 |df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Honor Thy Father ep\">{{Cite episode |title=Honor Thy Father |episode-link=Honor Thy Father (Arrow) |series=Arrow |series-link=Arrow (TV series) |network=[[The CW]] |season=1 |number=2 |airdate=October 17, 2012}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Bet